{"lemma":"سَعادَةٍ","slug":"سَعادَةٍ","root":"س.ع.د","root_slug":"س-ع-د","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ع-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19788"]}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَعِدَ (saʕida) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"happiness, gladness","examples":[{"text":"السَّعَادَةُ تَغْمُرُنِي.","english":"Happiness overwhelms me."},{"text":"a. 605, al-Nābighah al-Dhubiyānī\nوَٱلرِّفْقُ يُمْنٌ، وَٱلأَنَاةُ سَعَادَةٌ / فَٱسْتَأْنِ فِي رِفْقٍ تُلَاقِ نَجَاحَا\nwar-rifqu yumnun, wal-ʔanātu saʕādatun / fastaʔni fī rifqin tulāqi najāḥā","english":"Gentleness is a blessing; abiding is happiness. / So abide gently to find success."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"luck, good fortune"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bliss"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"prosperity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"highness, majesty (title)"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a surname"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of سَعِدَ (saʕida, “to be happy, to be lucky”)."},"ipa":["/sa.ʕaː.da/"]}